---
title: "Авторы блога"
description: "Команда экспертов SetHubble, которая делится знаниями о маркетинге, технологиях и росте бизнеса."
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /authors/index.html
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<section class="authors-page">
	<h1>{{ title }}</h1>
	<p class="authors-intro">{{ description }}</p>

	<div class="authors-grid">
		{%- for authorSlug, authorData in authors %}
		<article class="author-card">
			<div class="author-avatar">
				<img src="{{ authorData.image }}" alt="{{ authorData.name }}" width="120" height="120" loading="lazy">
			</div>
			<h2>{{ authorData.name }}</h2>
			<p class="author-bio">{{ authorData.bio }}</p>
			<a href="{{ authorData.url }}" class="author-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
				Перейти на сайт →
			</a>
		</article>
		{%- endfor %}
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.authors-page {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.authors-page h1 {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 15px;
	}
	.authors-intro {
		text-align: center;
		color: var(--text-gray);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto 50px;
	}
	.authors-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 30px;
	}
	.author-card {
		background: var(--card-bg);
		padding: 30px;
		border-radius: 20px;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		text-align: center;
		transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
	}
	.author-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		border-color: var(--primary);
	}
	.author-avatar {
		width: 120px;
		height: 120px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		overflow: hidden;
		margin: 0 auto 20px;
		border: 3px solid var(--primary);
	}
	.author-avatar img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
	}
	.author-card h2 {
		font-size: 1.4rem;
		margin: 0 0 15px 0;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}
	.author-bio {
		color: var(--text-gray);
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin-bottom: 20px;
	}
	.author-link {
		display: inline-block;
		color: var(--primary);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}
	.author-link:hover {
		color: var(--secondary);
	}
</style>
